xtras/4881c7748ea82008a6ae00983b19f367.mp4?t=1721750605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732290/extras/a606a724cd2b3583017da54d27273eac.avif?t=1721750605\" width=770 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732290/extras/49504a799f67bc444f924b3d410f1647.poster.avif?t=1721750605\" width=606 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732290/extras/49504a799f67bc444f924b3d410f1647.webm?t=1721750605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732290/extras/49504a799f67bc444f924b3d410f1647.mp4?t=1721750605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Important Note:</strong> I will definitely not add gambling to the game because money earned without effort has no value for me.<br><br><strong>Flea Market Simulator '24</strong> is all about buying and selling  flea market items. It is designed for trade and simulation game lovers.<br><br>You can purchase items from flea market. If you want to know more details about an item, you can ask to elder.<br><br>If you want to repair an item, go to the repair market and repair your items. <br><br>When you are ready to sell them, put them up for sale and wait your buyers. If you want to sell directly, sell it to the stores. <br><br>If you sell non-antique items as antique or if you gave wrong information to the buyers, they can call the police and you have to pay a fee.<br><br>Earn money and buy more expensive items, cars and many more!",
